Field Descriptions: This space is being used to store information, Narrative information,
Facility information, and Compound Ingredient Modifiers that are not
available elsewhere in the NCPDP format. Values are:
CMN - Follows Medicare required CMN or DIF information
CNA - Follows Medicare required CMN or DIF and narrative
information
CFA - Follows Medicare required CMN or DIF information and Facility
Name and Address
CNF - Follows Medicare required CMN or DIF information, narrative
information, and Facility Name and Address
FAC - Follows Medicare required Facility Name and address
FAN - Follows Medicare required Facility Name and Address and
narrative information
NAR - Follows Medicare required Narrative Information
MMN - Follows  Medicare modifier information and CMN or DIF
information
MNA - Follows  Medicare modifier information, CMN or DIF
information and narrative information
MFA - Follows  Medicare modifier information, CMN or DIF information
and Facility Name and Address
MNF - Follows  Medicare modifier information, CMN or DIF
information, narrative information and Facility Name and Address
MAC - Follows  Medicare modifier information and Facility Name and
Address
MAN - Follows  Medicare modifier information, narrative information
and Facility Name and Address
MAR - Follows  Medicare modifier information and narrative
information
MOD - Follows  Medicare modifier information
